<plot>This documentary follows the visit of the singer Chavela Vargas to the city of Guadalajara, as the guest of honor of the world premiere of the long feature documentary Hasta el último trago... corazón! During her visit, Chavela talks about lost nights and lost loves in that city. El primer trago con Chavela also contains info about the upcoming movie Salvar al soldado Pérez.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?172967</url></doc>
